cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use sottovoce, please cite the software and the accompanying paper."
title: "sottovoce: residual-stream confabulation detection and self-correction"
abstract: >-
  A lightweight probe that reads a language model's residual stream to detect
  when it has confabulated, transfers across architectures via a linear
  projection, and drives a two-pass self-correction loop.
type: software
authors:
